						<hi rend="italic">Nolite errare, Deus non</hi> irridetur: tile in <hi rend="italic">corde, non<lb/> videmus in facie (Gal.</hi> vi).</p>
					<p>Salomon loquitur in Proverbiis: <hi rend="italic">Ventus Aquilo <lb/> dissipat nubes,
